   20: -module(user_skip_6_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -compile(export_all).
   23: 
   24: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   25: 
   26: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   27: %% Function: suite() -> Info
   28: %% Info = [tuple()]
   29: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   30: suite() ->
   31:     [{timetrap,{seconds,30}}].
   32: 
   33: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   34: %% Function: init_per_group(GroupName, Config0) ->
   35: %%               Config1 | {skip,Reason} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
   36: %% GroupName = atom()
   37: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   38: %% Reason = term()
   39: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   40: init_per_group(ptop1, Config) ->
   41:     {skip,"Top group skipped"};
   42: init_per_group(psub2, Config) ->
   43:     {skip,"Sub group skipped"};
   44: init_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   45:     Config.
   46: 
   47: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   48: %% Function: end_per_group(GroupName, Config0) ->
   49: %%               void() | {save_config,Config1}
   50: %% GroupName = atom()
   51: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   52: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   53: end_per_group(_GroupName, _Config) ->
   54:     ok.
   55: 
   56: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   57: %% Function: init_per_testcase(TestCase, Config0) ->
   58: %%               Config1 | {skip,Reason} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
   59: %% TestCase = atom()
   60: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   61: %% Reason = term()
   62: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   63: init_per_testcase(_TestCase, Config) ->
   64:     Config.
   65: 
   66: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   67: %% Function: end_per_testcase(TestCase, Config0) ->
   68: %%               void() | {save_config,Config1}
   69: %% TestCase = atom()
   70: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   71: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   72: end_per_testcase(_TestCase, _Config) ->
   73:     ok.
   74: 
   75: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   76: %% Function: groups() -> [Group]
   77: %% Group = {GroupName,Properties,GroupsAndTestCases}
   78: %% GroupName = atom()
   79: %% Properties = [parallel | sequence | Shuffle | {RepeatType,N}]
   80: %% GroupsAndTestCases = [Group | {group,GroupName} | TestCase]
   81: %% TestCase = atom()
   82: %% Shuffle = shuffle | {shuffle,{integer(),integer(),integer()}}
   83: %% RepeatType = repeat | repeat_until_all_ok | repeat_until_all_fail |
   84: %%              repeat_until_any_ok | repeat_until_any_fail
   85: %% N = integer() | forever
   86: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   87: groups() ->
   88:     [{ptop1,[parallel],[tc1,{psub1,[parallel],[tc3,tc4]},tc2]},
   89:      {ptop2,[parallel],[tc1,{psub2,[parallel],[tc3,tc4]},tc2]}].
   90: 
   91: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   92: %% Function: all() -> GroupsAndTestCases | {skip,Reason}
   93: %% GroupsAndTestCases = [{group,GroupName} | TestCase]
   94: %% GroupName = atom()
   95: %% TestCase = atom()
   96: %% Reason = term()
   97: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   98: all() -> 
   99:     [{group,ptop1},{group,ptop2}].
  100: 
  101: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  102: %% Function: TestCase(Config0) ->
  103: %%               ok | exit() | {skip,Reason} | {comment,Comment} |
  104: %%               {save_config,Config1} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
  105: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
  106: %% Reason = term()
  107: %% Comment = term()
  108: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  109: tc1(_) ->
  110:     ok.
  111: 
  112: tc2(_) ->
  113:     ok.
  114: 
  115: tc3(_) ->
  116:     ok.
  117: 
  118: tc4(_) ->
  119:     ok.
